{"tid":1417884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非都可以係矛","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:46.000Z","uid":299742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e14726349360ae0f294caf4cb494b19d200b9798","tid":1417884,"uid":299742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"曾經講過勇武係矛，和理非做盾<br />\n到今時今日<br />\n和理非亦可以係矛，勇武亦可以係盾<br />\n<br />\n民間晨早講85罷工，點解政府就簡正呢日出黎記招，宣佈每日4點出招，分化前線同和理非同其他普通市民，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係因為政府都識驚</span>，驚經濟真係受影響，證明和理非方向無錯。<br />\n可能今次罷工成效未如理想，但係我地仲有下次或者下下次0既罷工，甚至大家發揮創意點樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\">罷市</span>，抵制消費，逼商家佬向政府施壓，曾經吉野家都可以係一個小例子。<br />\n<br />\n而家警黑勾結，刀手橫行，可以下次遊行完，坐地鐵行街野餐都會比人斬，無人話要勇武退場，但亦可以做保鏢做盾0既身份<br />\n<br />\n大家都唔想輸，，一味和理非或者一味勇武都會失敗，需要大家適時變化，真正be water。<br />\n<br />\n利申：sor for 1999兼新會員，抱有夢想，唔想輸"},{"pid":"55069b2628704ca860a359c589db34d0687b298f","tid":1417884,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcHFKYS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcHFKYS.png&h=79d7d376&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GqPDiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GqPDiS.png&h=a56dfa48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/012743_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F012743_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=f355d03a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/012744_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F012744_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=5d1f208c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/012745_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbna